    "We have observed that methods dealing with alignment issues (with the exception of the generation of toxic content, which in some cases can be tackled with the same mechanisms for privacy and copyright issues) have garnered less attention in the literature.",
    "As discussed above, a possible reason is that defining what is and what is not undesirable knowledge is difficult in the alignment scenario.",
    "Most methods, therefore, offer at most approximate guarantees; even in this case, the empirical evaluation of the unlearning performance is not well established.",
    "We now discuss the limitations of ex ante guarantees of forgetting.",
    "The forgetting guarantees presented in Sect. 2.3 were mainly devised for general neural network classifiers."
